Evening! Here is your in-class activity for the night, copied from Canvas:

For your In-Class Activity time:
• Pair up with someone else in your TA’s group. You will be working with this person for the duration of the in-class activity. Keep an eye on time so you both have an opportunity to interview. 
• Take turns conducting mini mock interviews. <https://docs.google.com/document/d/1j57lSMPZn5E2BQusDTrMHq8_QfzZRFbvZi1yL3FtuLM/edit?usp=sharing|Use the Interview Guide provided here>
    ◦ Select 3 questions from each section. 
    ◦ After the interview is done, discuss feedback. Talk through strengths, ways to improve, and any other general observations. 
• Switch roles.
I will have Zoom randomly pair you in breakout rooms and I will set a timer for 30 minutes.

Following this, 5-minute meetings will go in this order:
1. NCJS
2. Lambros
3. 404-found
